---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="AI Automation for Engineering Teams" description="Brandon Woodward — Systems Architect & AI Automation Consultant. I help engineering teams cut manual ops and integrate AI tooling that actually works.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">Systems Architecture &amp; AI Automation</div>
      <h1>
        Stop running your team<br />
        on <span class="accent">manual work.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        I help engineering teams cut ops toil and integrate AI tooling into real workflows —
        not demos, not pilots. Systems that run in production.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Discovery Call &nbsp;→</a>
        <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline">See Services</a>
      </div>
      <div class="social-proof">
        <span>20+ years engineering</span>
        <span class="dot">&middot;</span>
        <span>Rackspace &nbsp;·&nbsp; Amazon &nbsp;·&nbsp; Salesforce GovCloud</span>
        <span class="dot">&middot;</span>
        <span>FedRAMP-cleared environments</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain points -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Sound familiar?</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Your team is capable.<br />Your systems are holding them back.</h2>
      <div class="pain-grid">
        <div class="card pain-card">
          <div class="pain-icon">01</div>
          <h3>Manual toil stealing sprint capacity</h3>
          <p>Your engineers are spending hours on deploys, incident response, and runbooks that should be automated. That time belongs in your roadmap.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card pain-card">
          <div class="pain-icon">02</div>
          <h3>AI that doesn't connect to your systems</h3>
          <p>You've tried AI tools. They work in isolation but don't plug into your actual infrastructure. You need architecture, not another SaaS subscription.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card pain-card">
          <div class="pain-icon">03</div>
          <h3>Architecture decisions made without expertise</h3>
          <p>Hiring a senior systems architect full-time costs $250K+. You need that expertise for specific decisions, not a permanent headcount.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What I do -->
  <section class="section what-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="what-inner">
        <div class="what-text">
          <div class="section-label">What I do</div>
          <h2>Architecture that runs.<br /><span class="accent">AI that earns its keep.</span></h2>
          <p>
            I design systems that automate real operational work — the CI/CD toil, the runbook
            theater, the alert noise — and integrate AI where it delivers measurable throughput,
            not where it looks impressive in a slide deck.
          </p>
          <p>
            My background spans infrastructure at Rackspace, AWS IAM, RDS, and a decade at
            Salesforce GovCloud building security tooling for FedRAMP environments. I write Go,
            Python, and Bash. I deploy with Terraform and Ansible. I've run Kubernetes at scale.
          </p>
          <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">More about my background →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="what-stack">
          <div class="stack-card card">
            <div class="stack-label">Languages</div>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Go</span><span class="tag">Python</span><span class="tag">Bash</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="stack-card card">
            <div class="stack-label">Infrastructure</div>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Terraform</span><span class="tag">Ansible</span>
              <span class="tag">Kubernetes</span><span class="tag">Docker</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="stack-card card">
            <div class="stack-label">Cloud &amp; Compliance</div>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">AWS</span><span class="tag">FedRAMP</span>
              <span class="tag">GovCloud</span><span class="tag">PKI</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="stack-card card">
            <div class="stack-label">Observability</div>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Prometheus</span><span class="tag">Grafana</span>
              <span class="tag">Alertmanager</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services preview -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Engagements</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Three ways to work together.</h2>
      <div class="services-preview">
        <div class="card service-preview-card">
          <div class="service-badge">Entry point</div>
          <h3>Discovery Audit</h3>
          <p>A deep-dive into your current systems. Walk away with a written report of automation opportunities and an AI integration roadmap.</p>
          <div class="service-price">From $2,000</div>
          <a href="/services#discovery" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem;">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card service-preview-card featured">
          <div class="service-badge accent-badge">Most common</div>
          <h3>Project Engagement</h3>
          <p>Design and build one specific automation or AI integration — from architecture to production delivery.</p>
          <div class="service-price">$10,000–25,000</div>
          <a href="/services#project" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem;">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card service-preview-card">
          <div class="service-badge">Ongoing</div>
          <h3>Advisory Retainer</h3>
          <p>Async architecture guidance and a monthly strategy call. Senior systems expertise on demand without the headcount.</p>
          <div class="service-price">$3,000/mo</div>
          <a href="/services#retainer" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem;">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-inner card">
        <h2>Ready to automate what's slowing you down?</h2>
        <p>Start with a 30-minute conversation. No pitch deck. Just an honest look at where automation and AI can move the needle for your team.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Free Intro Call →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding: 6rem 0 5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--dim);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .social-proof {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .dot { opacity: 0.4; }

  /* Pain section */
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .pain-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .pain-card { position: relative; }

  .pain-icon {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: monospace;
  }

  .pain-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .pain-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* What I do */
  .what-section { background: var(--surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }

  .what-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .what-text h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.25rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  .what-text p { color: var(--dim); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .what-stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }

  .stack-card { padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; }

  .stack-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }

  .tag {
    background: rgba(63, 185, 80, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(63, 185, 80, 0.25);
    color: var(--accent);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Services preview */
  .services-preview {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .service-preview-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  .service-preview-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--accent), 0 8px 32px rgba(63, 185, 80, 0.1);
  }

  .service-badge {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .accent-badge { color: var(--accent); }

  .service-preview-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }

  .service-preview-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted); flex: 1; line-height: 1.6; }

  .service-price {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section { padding-bottom: 6rem; }

  .cta-inner {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
    border-color: var(--border);
  }

  .cta-inner h2 { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.25rem); margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  .cta-inner p { color: var(--muted); max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .what-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .hero { padding: 3.5rem 0 3rem; }
  }
</style>
